<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/748439.The_Confederate_War"><img alt="The Confederate War: How Popular Will, Nationalism, and Military Strategy Could Not Stave Off Defeat" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1347367981l/748439._SX98_.jpg" />
