<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/87019.Race_and_Reunion"><img alt="Race and Reunion: The Civil War in American Memory" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1348806887l/87019._SX98_.jpg" />
