      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/trivia/work/48359-mothers-of-invention-women-of-the-slaveholding-south-in-the-american-ci">Trivia About Mothers of Invent...</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
        <div class="mediumText">No trivia or quizzes yet. <a href="/trivia/work/48359-mothers-of-invention-women-of-the-slaveholding-south-in-the-american-ci">Add some now &raquo;</a></div>
